  <h2>Step 7: Design options for the user interface (UI)</h2>
  <h3>UI design and iteration</h3>
  <p>The sitemap is realised in the form of hub pages, content pages and navigation structures - the UI that supports your topic content.</p>
  <h4>The navigation system</h4>
  <p>The IA templates and components are in the service manual under components and page types. They were all designed, tested and iterated mobile-first and have been found to be usable, accessible, robust, flexible and learnable. The page templates and components were designed to work as a coherent whole, not individually in isolation.</p>
